title: Week 16 Games of the Week, Gimmes, and Games That Need Games
description:
Benjamin, Kaelen, and Steven begin by dissecting the biggest matchups of the week, including Bills-Pats and Steelers-Chiefs, and highlight the Games That Need Games. Finally, they wrap everything up with Gimme a Reason, in which they deliver their takes on the rest of the Week 16 slate.

Hosts: Benjamin Solak and Kaelen Jones
Associate Producer: Stefan Anderson
Additional Production Supervision: Arjuna Ramgopal
